{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-012__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-012", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-012__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·012.1", "text_original": "野有死麕，白茅包之，有女懷春，吉士誘之。", "text_normalized": "野有死麕，白茅包之，有女懷春，吉士誘之。", "notes": "野有死麕 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-012__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-012", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-012__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·012.2", "text_original": "林有樸樕，野有死鹿，白茅純束，有女如玉。", "text_normalized": "林有樸樕，野有死鹿，白茅純束，有女如玉。", "notes": "野有死麕 Chinese stanza 2."}
